text: Marco Cecchinato and Matteo Donati were the defending champions but chose not to defend their title. Kevin Krawietz and Andreas Mies won the title after defeating Tomasz Bednarek and David Pel 6–4, 6–2 in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw * Qualifying Draw Sibiu Open - Doubles 2018 Doubles
